# RESTful Routes

| NAME | PATH | VERB | PURPOSE | MONGOOSE METHOD |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| INDEX | / | GET | list all food trucks | .find() |
| NEW | /new | GET | show new food truck form | n/a |
| CREATE | / | POST | create new food truck and redir | .create() |
| SHOW | /:id | GET | show info about food truck | .findById() |
| EDIT | /:id/edit | GET | show edit form for food truck | .findById() |
| UPATE | /:id | PUT | update food truck and redir | .findByIdAndUpdate() |
| DESTROY | /:id | DELETE | delete food truck and redir | .findByIdAndRemove() |
